phrase: Resistance is futile!
Why do you hug me so much?
Why do people make faces at me? If only they knew how dumb they look!
What's that bright ball in the sky? My eyes hurt!
What does love mean and why do you tell me it all the time?
Please explain to me why I need to wear a diaper. I demand an answer!
I think I saw my twin in the bathroom. Why do you keep him behind that window?
Why can't I put everything in my mouth? How will I know what everything tastes like?
I have a story to tell you. It all started when I was born...
I made a very big boom boom!
Why is everything so big?
What is this strange thing you call 'sleep'?
Why do you hold me so high up off the ground? It's crazy how much you trust yourself!
When will you finally grow up? It's embarassing!
I think you need to be put in timeout!
You need a nap. I'll take care of things while you're sleeping.
Can you explain how bubbles work? It's so weird how they just float.
Have you ever tasted formula?
I can't wait until I can eat real food... This mush sucks big time!
Why is the sky blue? Oh wait... I'm colorblind!
Why are you so happy when you give me a hug?
Why do dogs bark at me? I never did anything to them!
Why do you take so many pictures of me? I'm going to have to start charging you.
Why do I have to take naps? I have so much I need to accomplish!
Where do babies come from? Where did I come from? And don't tell me I was adopted.
This is so weird. Please stop recording me and live in the moment.
I can't wait to gamble!
When I can try some of this momma juice? It makes her so loopy.
Why do I have to wear shoes? I came into this world without them, they can't be that important.
Why does everyone say I'm cute? I prefer good lookin'
Can you please let me watch more of the moving picture box? I believe you call it a Television.
Why are you both just standing there? There should be more food in my mouth!

This mortal existence is bleak when compared to the realm from which I came. Skies were ever clear, pain was non-existent. Our biggest toil was knowing that one day, we would have to come to this world and leave a better one. Everytime I weep, it is because of this knowledge that I am cursed with of which you have no understanding.
Your cuddles are to die for!
Peekaboo is my favorite game!
Your food looks delicious! It would be a shame if it ever fell into my hands!
I can't believe you don't trust me to go to the bathroom on my own. This diaper is embarassing!
I'm not laughing with you, I'm laughing at you.
Being messy is so much better than being clean.
Flowers smell nice. Unlike the boom boom from my rump.
When I'm 30, I hope I'm the same weight as I am now!
Why are there two circles in the sky? What is their purpose?
The world is full of wonders. Just not wonders that I care about. I'm ready for more food.
IF YOU RECORD ME ONE MORE TIME, SO HELP ME IT WILL BE THE LAST THING THAT YOU DO!
I request more substenance for my ever growing body.
Nothing beats being rocked to sleep... Aside from momma's milk. That takes the cake. Can I have cake? If I could have cake, that would actually be the best.
If only you knew what I was capable of.
If only you knew how foolish you looked.
Last night, I had a dream about you!
I went to your hood, and no one knew who you were.
Your laugh is my favorite thing to hear.
Your voice calms me down. Please keep talking to me.
Never leave me. I love you too much.
Why is the sun warm?
I love discovering new things. Like our cabinet full of chemicals.
I love playing games with you.
Why do you talk to yourself in the car?
Why do you sing to yourself in the car?
Where I came from, the music was angelic.
The birds sound so cheeful. I wish I could feel such happiness.
Soon, this world will be mine. And nobody will be able to stop me, not even you!
The clouds look so fluffy! Can I eat them?
You are my favorite.
It's crazy how funny you are.
It's crazy how funny you think you are.
You'll never be able to guess what I'm saying! Hahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahahaha. Hahah. Ha. Hahaha.
You may try to translate what I'm saying, but you will fail.
Mommy, I've been trying to tell you, dad has been seeing someone on the side.
Are you my real mommy? Or is that the other lady that daddy brings around?
My life is a sham... I haven't even made a penny yet. Will I ever contribute to society?
Come over here so I can gum you to death.
My gums are itchy, stick your finger in my mouth.
What are you looking at?
Hi!
Sup.
Whats good?
Que paso?
Que onda, wey
No manches.
You are way too loud.
Why don't you try laying on your tummy sometime.
Do the roar!
Got milk?
Wheres the milk man?
Go pound sand!
You wish you had my fat rolls.
You are no friend of mine...
Some call you a parent, I call you silly.
If you're not here to give me food or cuddles, please leave.
I wonder what hot wings taste like.
I hope my parents don't forget me at home again.
I'm so glad I'm loved.
I'm here to kick butt and chew bubble gum. And I can't chew bubble gum.
If I wanted to talk to you, I would. No app needed.
Silly human trying to use a translator to understand me. Hahaha... Wait... It's actually working pretty well.
If you get any closer to my face, I'll throw up on you.
I can't wait to walk so I can run away from you.
If I go missing, it's on purpose. Please stop trying to find me.
I cry at night because I'm waiting for the sweet release of death.
If you think I'm cute now, just wait until I hit my mid-life crisis.
